ame);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Does nothing.\n     */\n    public void close() {\n    }\n\n    public String toString() {\n        return thisClass.getName() + \".class\";\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777407500474}]}
